==================================================================
OUTPUT
==================================================================

The React application is successfully developed using Vite and integrated with GitHub, Jenkins, Docker, and Kubernetes. Jenkins automatically triggers the CI/CD pipeline using cron jobs, builds the React application, creates the Docker image, and deploys the application successfully on Kubernetes.
